	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus et pax Christi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">O deus, quantum exhilerasti me literis tuis<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Nicht erhalten.</note> ob felicissima ista nuntia de sopita contentione inter fratres <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernenses</placeName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Zur <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berner</placeName> Synode von Ende Mai s. die Berichte <persName ref="p8412" cert="high">Meganders</persName> oben <ref target="file11041">Nr. 999</ref>, 16-21, und unten <ref target="file11052">Nr. 1010</ref>, 1-65.</note> et extincto Arianismi incendio<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Vgl. die von <persName ref="p8412" cert="high">Megander</persName> übermittelten und durch <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullinger</persName> auch an <persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Vadian</persName> weitergeleiteten Nachrichten über die Lausanner Synode vom 14. Mai und den Widerruf des Antitrinitariers <persName ref="p7242" cert="high">Claude d'Aliod</persName>, oben <ref target="file11041">Nr. 999</ref>, 9-15, bzw. <ref target="file11049">Nr. 1007</ref>.</note> optimoque illo in<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">in <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note> <placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglia</placeName> successu<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Gemeint ist die Niederschlagung des Aufstandes, der als "Pilgrimage of Grace" in die Geschichte einging; vgl. oben <ref target="file11026">Nr. 984</ref> und 1007.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino sint perpetuae gratiae, quod semper adstet nobis!</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miraris autem, cur ego ad te nihil.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed quid fingam, mi frater, si veri nihil sit prae manibus?</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non sum tam natus ad fingendum.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Patienter feras itaque silentium, donec aliqua sit scribendi occasio, quam nunc ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> et <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorato</placeName> expecto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Unum hoc iam volo, ut, si possis, impedias <persName ref="p7242" cert="high">Claudium <span type="affix">illum</span> Sabaudum</persName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p7242" cert="high">Claude d'Aliod</persName>.</note>, ne ad nos veniat aut alias ecclesias de nostris; non enim efficiet quicquam, nisi quod in memoriam<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>vor</hi> memoriam <hi>gestrichenes</hi> re.</note> revocabit priora<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>vor</hi> priora <hi>gestrichenes</hi> p.</note><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="p7242" cert="high">D'Aliod</persName> war 1534 wegen seiner Lehre aus <placeName ref="l257" cert="high">Konstanz</placeName> ausgewiesen worden; s. <persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Vadian</persName> BW V 182f.</note>, ut credam minus profuturum<pb type="edition" next="175"/> illius ad nostros adventum.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si viatico opus est illi, numera<note xml:id="fnd" type="footnote" n="d"><hi>vor</hi> numera <hi>gestrichenes</hi> d.</note> dimidium aureum, quem ego restituam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc tumultuanter; nam <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basiliensis</placeName> contionator <persName ref="p8466" cert="high">Wolfgangus</persName><note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="p8466" cert="high">Wolfgang Wissenburg</persName>.</note> apud nos est, quocum cogor tempus absumere.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De aliis proxime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale diutissime cum tota familia et bonis omnibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">19. iunii 1537.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Io. Zwick</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vigilantissimo Christi ministro d. <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Hainricho Bullingero</persName>, et domino et fratri suo studiosissime colendo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
